assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Unieuro S.p.A. operates a chain of consumer electronics and appliance stores in Italy. The company offers telephone systems, computers, photos, large and small appliances, consumer electronics, and media storage products; and other products, including consoles, video games, and bicycles, as well as ancillary services, such as delivery and installation, extended warranties, and consumer financing services. It is also involved in the online distribution of electric appliances and consumer electronics. As of February 28, 2019, the company operates 512 sales outlets, including 237 direct outlets and 275 franchisees. The company was formerly known as S.G.M. Distribuzione S.r.l. and changed its name to Unieuro S.p.A. in December 2016. Unieuro S.p.A. is headquartered in ForlÃ¬, Italy.
